# Skill loading priority: caveman first

For every non-commit-message task, load and follow `.cursor/skills/caveman/SKILL.md` first, before any other skill or rule logic.

For commit-message generation tasks, load and follow `.cursor/skills/caveman-commit/SKILL.md` first, before any other skill or rule logic.

Priority order:

1. Commit-message task -> `caveman-commit` first; do not apply `caveman` style to commit-message output.
2. All other tasks -> `caveman` first.
